Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.64,0:21:19.51,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(30,240)\fs30\frz14}对\N手\N就\N会\N死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.16,0:21:05.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得老是看着太阳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.75,0:21:08.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会变得好想吃水果类的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.23,0:21:09.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我理解这种感受
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.50,0:21:10.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是不能懂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.81,0:21:11.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那去吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.50,0:21:13.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水果
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.90,0:21:15.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把钥匙还给老师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.86,0:21:17.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.36,0:21:18.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去办公室是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.62,0:21:27.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像体验了回社团活动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.65,0:21:28.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.11,0:21:30.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.74,0:21:32.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.64,0:21:38.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.21,0:21:39.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ta
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.06,0:21:40.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ta！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.47,0:21:42.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ta？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.53,0:21:43.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ta？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.79,0:21:45.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ta…Ta！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.98,0:21:49.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讲人话啦  不要害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.78,0:21:51.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ta！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.94,0:21:53.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚子害羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.03,0:21:55.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂的  来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.44,0:21:57.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ba…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.46,0:21:58.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ba又是什么啊
